es/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3dce802066d0aa1dd13adfa242c964c08ce66e3","tid":92773,"uid":2316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:08:17.000Z","msg":"個仔幾時死"},{"pid":"60120c02351423a56d82d35a857563934e6a8039","tid":92773,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:13:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實學校本身就分左級數，咪正係俾優秀的學校參與TSA。其他屋邨學校，band3學校，話驚個細路辛苦壓力點點，咪叫佢哋唔好參加，由9佢。</blockquote><br />\n其實主要想講係過份操練嘅問題 呢方面全香港避無可避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗名校英中唔會抗拒呢D嘢，叫生叫死的應該都係普通學校學生及家長。咁咪俾精英的更精英，班廢的就由佢哋自生自滅囉，由佢哋愉快學習，乜嘢都唔好學，生字唔洗串。反正社會都係需要好多數量的基層勞動力去做嘢。"},{"pid":"2d2ebbad09168ab4a5749ed347a46c799af20e58","tid":92773,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:14:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51ebdf166a5fb6448d0c42c6391c852574ca8b4c","tid":92773,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:25:48.000Z","msg":"新年流流 唔好講衰野啦<br />\n祝吳克儉一家齊齊整整 早日團圓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6091ca26133b2a1f7e604619e19fac0fc765e8c9","tid":92773,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:28:34.000Z","msg":"老婆得一個，辭職陪老婆過埋餘下日子<br />\n你嘅生活費林大輝會幫你籌架啦"},{"pid":"8de0b534f01667f1f85887963d49c35908cd164d","tid":92773,"uid":10397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老婆得一個，辭職陪老婆過埋餘下日子<br />\n你嘅生活費林大輝會幫你籌架啦</blockquote><br />\n老婆老母都死哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落去陪就岩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017b178a7edf117a1d86dbd6c366875e6c5f429f","tid":92773,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01